get.description: Specify query parameters to return sales quotes.

parameters.name: $top
parameters.description: Show only the first n sales quotes.

parameters.name: $skip
parameters.description: Skip the first n sales quotes.

parameters.name: $search
parameters.description: Search for a string within sales quote.

one.summary: Order sales quotes by name in ascending order.

parameters.name: $count
parameters.description: Indicates if count of sales quotes to be returned.

parameters.name: $query
parameters.description: Indicates the query to be used by sales quote service.
